name: GetThe Cake
description:
THERE IS YOUR FRIEND'S BIRTH DAY.

BUT HE DOESN'T HAVE  THE CAKE.

SO YOU GO TO GET IT.

YOU WILL GO THROUGH A LITTLE ADVENTURE TO GET IT.

AND YOU FIND  OUT THAT THERE IS A CAKE BUT YOU NEED THE KEY AND  IT'S CHEST. TO GET THE CAKE

P.S. DON'T BELIEVE EVERYTHING IS WHAT YOU THINK IT IS!
